OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and breezy across much of
OL,6,Fthe region, although some light rain
OL,7,Fpossible across the Derbyshire hills
OL,8,Fduring the early morning. Plenty of
OL,9,Fsunny spells, especially through the
OL,10,Fafternoon. Temperatures around, or
OL,11,Fslightly above, average.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA pleasant evening with
OL,14,Fwidespread sunshine and easing winds
OL,15,Ffor many, followed by a mostly clear
OL,16,Fnight. Remaining breezy along coasts.
OL,17,
OL,18,CFriday:FCloudy through the morning on
OL,19,FFriday, sunnier spells developing more
OL,20,Fwidely through the afternoon and
OL,21,Fevening. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
