OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fand breezy for much of the period,
OL,7,Fstaying mostly dry although the odd
OL,8,Fspot of rain is possible in the
OL,9,Fnorthwest. Temperatures probably above
OL,10,Faverage.
